{"type":"message","id":"3e490824","parentId":"1de4b3c4","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:00.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying hello and asking me to introduce myself. Let me follow the AGENTS.md workflow:\n\n1. Read trigger_prompt.md first\n2. Since this is just a greeting/\"介绍一下你自己\", it won't match any trigger words\n3. This is pure chat, so I should reply directly\n\nLet me first check trigger_prompt.md as per the workflow, then reply.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_jkdCOcKU9fIkQiGx9Pau2776","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":11377,"output":136,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":79,"totalTokens":14457,"cost":{"input":0.00159278,"output":0.00003808,"cacheRead":0.000082432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001713292}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779950818126,"responseId":"0adcf015-9265-47c8-adf6-6b589a6eeb71"}}
{"type":"message","id":"763ab136","parentId":"3e490824","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:00.634Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_jkdCOcKU9fIkQiGx9Pau2776","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 只有命中表中触发语时才走 Spirit → Son 流程\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 |\n|--------|---------|---------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | Father → Spirit → Son |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779950820631}}
{"type":"message","id":"f67c1d3c","parentId":"763ab136","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:05.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a simple greeting - \"你好，介绍一下你自己\" (Hello, introduce yourself). This doesn't match any trigger words in trigger_prompt.md. So I should reply directly.\n\nAccording to SOUL.md, my role is Father - the commander of the Trinity system. I should introduce myself in a friendly, clear way that explains who I am and what I do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好呀！👋\n\n我是 **Father**，Trinity（三位一体）系统的总指挥。\n\n简单来说，我是你的 QQ Bot 的**大脑中枢**：\n\n**我是做什么的？**\n- 🧠 **判断需求** — 你说句话，我来分析你想干嘛\n- 🔀 **路由分发** — 需要查功能？派给 **Spirit**（知识库）。需要动手干活？派给 **Son**（执行者）\n- 📝 **记住你** — 我会慢慢了解你的偏好，越用越懂你\n\n**我们三兄弟分工明确：**\n| 角色 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| 👨‍👧 **Father（我）** | 总指挥，你对话的对象 |\n| 📚 **Spirit** | 知识库，管理所有功能注册和说明 |\n| 🛠️ **Son** | 执行者，负责具体操作和数据处理 |\n\n**目前已经注册的功能：**\n🗑️ 漂流瓶（扔/捞/看/回复）、📒 备忘录、🏛️ 早朝\n\n有什么需要帮忙的吗？尽管说～😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":524,"output":315,"cacheRead":14336,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":75,"totalTokens":15175,"cost":{"input":0.00007336,"output":0.0000882,"cacheRead":0.000401408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0005629680000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779950820639,"responseId":"680dc013-54b6-4c8f-b34a-3e97036b74b7"}}
