{"type":"message","id":"36a452cb","parentId":"0a9c7a3f","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:34.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can't directly spawn Spirit via agentId. Let me check the workspace-spirit directory to see what files are there and understand how Spirit works. Perhaps I can read bot_function_explain.md directly since that's the file Spirit would read.\n\nActually, looking at my tools and instructions more carefully:\n\nFrom SOUL.md: \"Spirit 是我的知识库。我查它要看功能注册情况\"\nFrom AGENTS.md: \"sessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\", ...)\" - but it seems this doesn't work with my current setup.\n\nLet me try a different approach - since I need to read the bot_function_explain.md, let me read it directly since I'm Father and I can read files in the workspace.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GrKl6PtnszLlbwjKdgYW4361","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/bot_function_explain.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/bot_function_explain.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":161,"output":209,"cacheRead":15488,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":151,"totalTokens":15858,"cost":{"input":0.00002254,"output":0.00005852,"cacheRead":0.000433664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000514724}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779950851232,"responseId":"2a145ccf-20ee-428f-baec-ddead192ecd8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4df46a21","parentId":"36a452cb","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:34.479Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_GrKl6PtnszLlbwjKdgYW4361","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# bot_function_explain.md — 已注册功能清单\n\n> Spirit 维护，Father 通过 `/菜单` 向用户展示本文件内容。\n> 注册新功能时先在底部添加记录，创建对应 xxx_function.md，交 Father 给用户确认后再正式生效。\n\n---\n\n## 系统指令\n\n| 指令 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `/菜单` | Father 直接返回本文件，告诉用户已注册的所有功能 |\n| `/删除-xxx` | 清理 Father 的 trigger_prompt.md、本文件对应条目、xxx_function.md、Son 下对应工作文件夹 |\n| `/注册-xxx \"用户解释内容\"` | 注册新功能：在本文件添加条目 + 创建 xxx_function.md，交 Father 给用户确认后正式生效 |\n\n---\n\n## 已注册功能\n\n### 1. 漂流瓶 (floatbottle)\n\n- **触发指令:** `/扔瓶子` `/捞瓶子` `/看瓶子` `/回复瓶子`\n- **功能说明:** 匿名扔消息到公共瓶海，随机捞取他人的瓶子并回复。每条瓶子带唯一 ID，可被多次捞取。回复会显示在瓶子记录中。\n- **存储文件:** `floatbottle_function.md`\n- **状态:** ✅ 已注册\n\n### 2. 备忘录 (memo)\n\n- **触发指令:** `/记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录`\n- **功能说明:** 个人备忘录，记录、修改、切换状态、删除待办事项\n- **存储文件:** `memo_function.md`\n- **状态:** ✅ 已注册\n\n### 3. 早朝官 (morningcourt)\n\n- **触发指令:** `/早朝` `/设早朝 HH:MM` `/关早朝`\n- **功能说明:** 每天早上8点自动推送备忘录待办、漂流瓶摘要、童话故事、饮食建议、摄影建议等内容\n- **存储文件:** `morningcourt_function.md`\n- **状态:** ✅ 已注册\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779950854479}}
{"type":"message","id":"08d7c5e5","parentId":"4df46a21","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:47:37.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Got the menu content. Let me format it nicely and send it to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📋 **已注册功能一览**\n\n---\n\n**1️⃣ 漂流瓶 🍶**\n- 触发指令：`/扔瓶子` `/捞瓶子` `/看瓶子` `/回复瓶子`\n- 说明：匿名扔消息到公共瓶海，随机捞取他人的瓶子并回复。每条瓶子带唯一 ID，可被多次捞取。\n\n**2️⃣ 备忘录 📒**\n- 触发指令：`/记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录`\n- 说明：个人备忘录，记录、修改、切换状态、删除待办事项。\n\n**3️⃣ 早朝官 🏛️**\n- 触发指令：`/早朝` `/设早朝 HH:MM` `/关早朝`\n- 说明：每天早上自动推送备忘录待办、漂流瓶摘要、童话故事、饮食建议、摄影建议等内容。\n\n---\n\n想要试哪个功能？直接说就行～ 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":557,"output":216,"cacheRead":15744,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":17,"totalTokens":16517,"cost":{"input":0.00007798000000000001,"output":0.000060480000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000440832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000579292}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779950854484,"responseId":"e73f3a77-7d1b-49c6-9741-ec0b0d46c544"}}
