{"type":"message","id":"ae3eba5b","parentId":"aecb5cdf","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:48:18.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sub-agent has completed successfully and returned \"子 agent 调用成功 ✅\". Let me tell the user the result.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**子 agent 调用测试结果：**\n\n子 agent 成功被 spawn ✅，返回了预期结果：\n> **\"子 agent 调用成功 ✅\"**\n\n完整链路跑通了！整体流程：\n1. ✅ `sessions_spawn` 成功创建子 agent\n2. ✅ `sessions_yield` 成功等待子 agent 完成\n3. ✅ 子 agent 执行任务并返回结果\n4. ✅ 结果成功回传到父 agent\n\n不过这里要说明一下：AGENTS.md 里写的 `sessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\")` 这种方式目前走不通（agentId 被限制为仅 `father`），但通过 `runtime=\"subagent\"` 的方式可以灵活创建子 agent 来执行任务，效果是一样的 👍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":14028,"output":189,"cacheRead":2944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":24,"totalTokens":17161,"cost":{"input":0.00196392,"output":0.00005292,"cacheRead":0.000082432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002099272}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779950894421,"responseId":"823f7d06-e21a-4437-933d-139ce6781370"}}
