{"type":"message","id":"3b0ce554","parentId":"be954bdd","timestamp":"2026-05-28T06:49:47.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the architecture: can Father spawn Spirit, and then can Spirit spawn Son?\n\nLooking at my AGENTS.md, the intended architecture is:\n\n1. Father receives message\n2. Father spawns Spirit to interpret/understand\n3. Father spawns Son to execute\n4. Father relays results back\n\nBut the issue is that `sessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\")` didn't work - agentId is restricted. Let me think about this...\n\nFrom my testing just now, I can spawn sub-agents via `sessions_spawn` with `runtime=\"subagent\"`. So the question is really about the workflow architecture.\n\nIn the AGENTS.md, the intended flow is:\n- Father → Spirit (for knowledge/interpretation)\n- Father → Son (for execution)\n\nBut actually, looking at AGENTS.md section 3.3:\n```\nStep 1: spawn Spirit → 传入用户消息 → Spirit 找到对应的 xxx_function.md → Spirit 解析用户意图，组装执行指令给 Son\nStep 2: spawn Son → 传入 Spirit 组装的执行指令 → Son 按 xxx_function.md 执行 → Son 返回结果\nStep 3: 转发结果\n```\n\nSo the intended flow is actually sequential: Father spawns Spirit first, gets the result, then Father spawns Son with the instructions from Spirit. It's not Spirit directly spawning Son.\n\nLet me explain this clearly to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！让我根据当前的实际测试结果和架构设计说一下：\n\n---\n\n## 当前实际情况\n\n**Father → 子 agent ✅**（已测试通过）\n\n但 Father 不能通过 `agentId: \"spirit\"` 或 `agentId: \"son\"` 来定向召唤——当前 `sessions_spawn` 的 agentId 参数被限制为仅允许 `father`。\n\n---\n\n## 实际工作流程是怎样的\n\n按照 AGENTS.md 的设计，**不是 Spirit 直接 spawn Son**，而是 **Father 分两步走**：\n\n```\n你发消息 → Father 判断命中功能\n              │\n              ├─ Step 1: Father spawn 子 agent 当 Spirit\n              │    → Spirit 查 xxx_function.md\n              │    → Spirit 返回\"执行指令\"\n              │\n              ├─ Step 2: Father 拿到指令后，再 spawn 另一个子 agent 当 Son\n              │    → 传入 Spirit 给的指令\n              │    → Son 执行具体操作\n              │    → Son 返回结果\n              │\n              └─ Step 3: Father 把结果转发给你\n```\n\n## 一个具体例子\n\n```\n你说：「扔瓶子 今天天气真好」\n\nFather:\n  → spawn 子 agent①（Spirit 角色）\n     → 查 floatbottle_function.md\n     → 返回：「指令: 存入瓶子, 内容: 今天天气真好」\n\nFather 拿到结果后:\n  → spawn 子 agent②（Son 角色）\n     → 传入：「存入瓶子, 内容: 今天天气真好」\n     → Son 写入瓶子数据文件\n     → 返回：「瓶子已扔出 ✅ 编号 #42」\n\nFather → 转发给你：「瓶子已扔出 ✅ 编号 #42」\n```\n\n## 总结\n\n| 问 | 答 |\n|---|-----|\n| Father 能 spawn 子 agent？ | ✅ 可以 |\n| Spirit 能 spawn Son？ | ❌ 不能，是 Father 来协调 |\n| 实际链路？ | **Father → 子 agent①(Spirit) → 再 spawn 子 agent②(Son)** |\n\n所以我是中枢协调器，所有 spawn 都从我这儿发出。Spirit 负责**出脑力**（查知识、组装指令），Son 负责**出体力**（读写文件、干活），我负责**调度**。三位一体，各司其职 👍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2350,"output":812,"cacheRead":14848,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":298,"totalTokens":18010,"cost":{"input":0.00032900000000000003,"output":0.00022736000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000415744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0009721040000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779950975859,"responseId":"545857c4-a340-421e-92d6-9916d1920d36"}}
