{"type":"message","id":"f4b31b0e","parentId":"c0efb2d7","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:02:20.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to reconfigure the system according to the Trinity.md design. Specifically:\n\n1. Father (agentId: father) - already configured, has agentId\n2. Spirit (agentId: spirit) - needs agentId permission so it can spawn Son\n3. Son (agentId: son) - needs agentId permission so it can be targeted by Spirit\n\nLet me first check the current openclaw.json configuration to understand how agents are currently set up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我先看看当前 `openclaw.json` 的配置，按照 Trinity.md 的设计来调整。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_lZSkcy6C2VMxvBQVPkyg7589","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6535,"output":171,"cacheRead":18304,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":97,"totalTokens":25010,"cost":{"input":0.0009149000000000001,"output":0.00004788,"cacheRead":0.000512512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001475292}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779951737406,"responseId":"3cd80a92-80b5-41bf-8e3d-29df1ef6b4a8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e335144","parentId":"f4b31b0e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:02:20.695Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_lZSkcy6C2VMxvBQVPkyg7589","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\",\n      \"subagents\": {\n        \"delegationMode\": \"prefer\",\n        \"maxSpawnDepth\": 2,\n        \"maxConcurrent\": 5,\n        \"runTimeoutSeconds\": 300,\n        \"maxChildrenPerAgent\": 5,\n        \"archiveAfterMinutes\": 15\n      },\n      \"models\": {\n        \"deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash\": {\n          \"alias\": \"DeepSeek\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"default\": true,\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"father\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"son\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-son\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"spirit\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"auth\": {\n      \"mode\": \"token\",\n      \"token\": \"46aeff…9163\"\n    },\n    \"port\": 18789,\n    \"bind\": \"loopback\",\n    \"tailscale\": {\n      \"mode\": \"off\",\n      \"resetOnExit\": false\n    },\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"allowInsecureAuth\": true\n    },\n    \"nodes\": {\n      \"denyCommands\": [\n        \"camera.snap\",\n        \"camera.clip\",\n        \"screen.record\",\n        \"contacts.add\",\n        \"calendar.add\",\n        \"reminders.add\",\n        \"sms.send\",\n        \"sms.search\"\n      ]\n    }\n  },\n  \"session\": {\n    \"dmScope\": \"per-channel-peer\"\n  },\n  \"tools\": {\n    \"sessions_spawn\": {},\n    \"profile\": \"coding\",\n    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"provider\": \"kimi\",\n        \"enabled\": true\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"plugins\": {\n    \"entries\": {\n      \"deepseek\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"qqbot\": {\n        \"enabled\": true\n      },\n      \"moonshot\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"config\": {\n          \"webSearch\": {\n            \"apiKey\": \"sk-slC…qx49\"\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"models\": {\n    \"mode\": \"merge\",\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"deepseek\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.deepseek.com\",\n        \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n            \"name\": \"DeepSeek V4 Flash\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\"\n            ],\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"input\": 0.14,\n              \"output\": 0.28,\n              \"cacheRead\": 0.028,\n              \"cacheWrite\": 0\n            },\n            \"contextWindow\": 1000000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 384000,\n            \"compat\": {\n              \"supportsReasoningEffort\": true,\n              \"supportsUsageInStreaming\": true,\n              \"maxTokensField\": \"max_tokens\"\n            },\n            \"api\": \"openai-completions\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"deepseek-v4-pro\",\n            \"name\": \"DeepSeek V4 Pro\",\n            \"reasoning\": true,\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\"\n            ],\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"input\": 1.74,\n              \"output\": 3.48,\n              \"cacheRead\": 0.145,\n              \"cacheWrite\": 0\n            },\n            \"contextWindow\": 1000000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 384000,\n            \"compat\": {\n              \"supportsReasoningEffort\": true,\n              \"supportsUsageInStreaming\": true,\n              \"maxTokensField\": \"max_