t:<agentId>:subagent:<uuid>`) and,\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/subagents.md:65:Agents start background sub-agents with `sessions_spawn`. Sub-agent completions\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/subagents.md:71:    - `sessions_spawn` is non-blocking; it returns a run id immediately.\n/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/tools/subagents.md:105:    - For persistent thread-bound sessions, use `sessions_spawn` with `thread: true` and `mode: \"session\"`.","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779951754399}}
