{"type":"message","id":"c46b2fdc","parentId":"9cafd972","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:03:19.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the current config. The key missing piece is `allowAgents`. Let me make the changes:\n\n1. Add `allowAgents: [\"*\"]` to the subagents defaults so any agent can spawn any other agent by agentId\n2. Keep `maxSpawnDepth: 2` as is (already correct for Father → Spirit → Son chain)\n\nWait, actually, let me think about this more carefully. The current `maxSpawnDepth: 2` means:\n- Main (depth 0) can spawn sub-agents (depth 1)\n- Those sub-agents (depth 1) can spawn sub-sub-agents (depth 2)\n\nBut the issue is with `allowAgents` - without it set, sessions_spawn can't use a different `agentId`.\n\nFrom the docs:\n> `agents.defaults.subagents.allowAgents`: Default configured target-agent allowlist used when the requester agent does not set its own `subagents.allowAgents`.\n\n> `agents.list[].subagents.allowAgents`: List of configured agent ids that can be targeted via explicit `agentId` (`[\"*\"]` allows any configured target). Default: only the requester agent.\n\nSo I need to add `allowAgents: [\"*\"]` (or specific agentIds) to make the system work.\n\nLet me also check the `tools.sessions_spawn` section in the current config - it's an empty object `{}`. Let me check the schema for what can be configured there.\n\nActually, let me just make the changes now. The plan per Trinity.md:\n\n**Config changes:**\n1. Add `\"allowAgents\": [\"*\"]` to `agents.defaults.subagents` - so Spirit can spawn Son\n2. Keep `maxSpawnDepth: 2` (already correct)\n\nThis should enable:\n- Father → sessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\") ✅\n- Spirit (as subagent) → sessions_spawn(agentId: \"son\") ✅\n\nLet me also check if I should add per-agent subagents configs for finer control. Per Trinity.md:\n- Father: needs to spawn Spirit and Son, but in the designed flow Father spawns Spirit, and Spirit spawns Son\n- Father can also spawn Son directly for non-text tasks (searches, images)\n- Spirit needs to spawn Son\n- Son should NOT spawn anything (leaf node)\n\nLet me keep it simple and just use the defaults with `allowAgents: [\"*\"]`.\n\nActually, I want to be precise. Let me update the config now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！现在按 **Trinity.md** 的顶层设计来修改配置。关键调整是：\n\n1. `maxSpawnDepth: 2` 已正确（允许 Father → Spirit → Son 两层）\n2. 缺少 `allowAgents` — 所以目前只有 father 能通过 agentId 被调用\n3. 需要加上，让 Spirit 能 spawn Son"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FI6Yb8VRJtTr2OEccNWb0911","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json","edits":[{"oldText":"\"subagents\": {\n    \"delegationMode\": \"prefer\",\n    \"maxSpawnDepth\": 2,\n    \"maxConcurrent\": 5,\n    \"runTimeoutSeconds\": 300,\n    \"maxChildrenPerAgent\": 5,\n    \"archiveAfterMinutes\": 15\n  }","newText":"\"subagents\": {\n    \"delegationMode\": \"prefer\",\n    \"maxSpawnDepth\": 2,\n    \"maxConcurrent\": 5,\n    \"runTimeoutSeconds\": 300,\n    \"maxChildrenPerAgent\": 5,\n    \"archiveAfterMinutes\": 15,\n    \"allowAgents\": [\"*\"]\n  }"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"\\\"subagents\\\": {\\n    \\\"delegationMode\\\": \\\"prefer\\\",\\n    \\\"maxSpawnDepth\\\": 2,\\n    \\\"maxConcurrent\\\": 5,\\n    \\\"runTimeoutSeconds\\\": 300,\\n    \\\"maxChildrenPerAgent\\\": 5,\\n    \\\"archiveAfterMinutes\\\": 15\\n  }\", \"newText\": \"\\\"subagents\\\": {\\n    \\\"delegationMode\\\": \\\"prefer\\\",\\n    \\\"maxSpawnDepth\\\": 2,\\n    \\\"maxConcurrent\\\": 5,\\n    \\\"runTimeoutSeconds\\\": 300,\\n    \\\"maxChildrenPerAgent\\\": 5,\\n    \\\"archiveAfterMinutes\\\": 15,\\n    \\\"allowAgents\\\": [\\\"*\\\"]\\n  }\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":85,"output":860,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":540,"totalTokens":47793,"cost":{"in