{"type":"message","id":"3e61b1f7","parentId":"2977b0b1","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:04:36.600Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The test was successful! The full chain worked:\n\n1. **Father** spawned a sub-agent as **Spirit** ✅\n2. **Spirit** read the workspace-spirit/bot_function_explain.md ✅\n3. **Spirit** successfully spawned a child sub-agent as **Son** ✅\n4. **Son** returned the test message ✅\n5. All results flowed back to Father ✅\n\nThe Trinity workflow is fully functional: **Father → Spirit → Son → Father** ✅","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🎉 全链路测试通过！\n\n**Father → Spirit → Son → Father 完整跑通！**\n\n```\n                 你（QQ）\n                   │\n               ┌───▼───┐\n               │ Father │  ← 收到 /菜单 请求\n               └───┬───┘\n                   │ sessions_spawn(agentId: \"father\") 作为 Spirit\n               ┌───▼───┐\n               │ Spirit │  ← 读 bot_function_explain.md ✅\n               │       │     再 sessions_spawn 子 agent 作为 Son\n               └───┬───┘\n                   │\n              ┌────▼────┐\n              │   Son   │  ← 执行成功 ✅ 返回结果\n              └────┬────┘\n                   │\n               ┌───▼───┐\n               │ Father │  ← 转发结果给你\n               └───┬───┘\n                   │\n                 你（QQ）\n```\n\n**测试结果明细：**\n\n| 环节 | 状态 |\n|------|:----:|\n| Father 收到 `/菜单` → spawn Spirit | ✅ |\n| Spirit 读 `bot_function_explain.md`（3 个功能） | ✅ |\n| Spirit spawn Son | ✅ |\n| Son 执行并返回结果 | ✅ |\n| 结果回传到 Father → 到你 | ✅ |\n\n**config 只改了一处：** `agents.defaults.subagents.allowAgents: [\"*\"]`，让子 agent 也可以按 agentId 定向 spawn 其他 agent（Spirit → Son）。\n\nTrinity 三层架构现在完全跑通了，整个信息流就是 Trinity.md 设计的：\n```\nFather（总指挥）→ Spirit（知识中枢→派活）→ Son（执行）→ 结果回流\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":40658,"output":493,"cacheRead":10752,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":101,"totalTokens":51903,"cost":{"input":0.