{"type":"message","id":"90da9128","parentId":"e59d8db2","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:05:07.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can process images. This doesn't match any trigger words in trigger_prompt.md, so it's a general chat question. I can reply directly.\n\nThe answer is: as Father, I can read images (using the `read` tool which supports jpg, png, gif, webp - it says \"Images are sent as attachments\"), but for more complex image processing like generation or manipulation, according to AGENTS.md, non-text tasks (like image generation/processing) should be sent to Son.\n\nLet me give a clear answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"能处理，分两种情况：\n\n### ✅ 我能直接做的\n- **看图读图** — 你用 `read` 工具读取图片（jpg/png/gif/webp），我能识别图片内容。\n- 比如你发一张截图给我，我能看懂上面写了什么。\n\n### 🔄 需要转 Son 的\n- **生成图片** — 比如你要我画一张图、生成海报等\n- **编辑/处理图片** — 加文字、裁剪、滤镜等\n- **搜图/找图** — 需要网页搜索图片\n\n这些非纯文本任务，按 Trinity 设计是交 **Son** 去执行。但流程上你觉得 **想直接发图给我看**，那就发过来，我先看看能不能看懂 👍\n\n你有图要发给我看看吗？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":31926,"output":288,"cacheRead":19712,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":117,"totalTokens":51926,"cost":{"input":0.00446964,"output":0.00008064,"cacheRead":0.0005519359999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0051022160000000006}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779951901024,"responseId":"d960b3dc-4a40-4be2-b343-2fbda1e4855b"}}
