{"type":"message","id":"2ed91e2b","parentId":"dba9c803","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:05:48.594Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that I don't have image generation configured yet. Let me check what the system can currently do and respond accordingly.\n\nLooking at the system:\n- We have the `meme-maker` skill available but that's for memes\n- There's no dedicated \"image generation\" function registered\n- My Son doesn't have tools like DALL-E, Stable Diffusion, etc.\n\nLet me check what's available for image generation - the available skills include `meme-maker` which handles meme generation, but for actual AI image generation, I'd need to check if there's a provider configured.\n\nLet me think about what I actually have:\n- No image generation API configured (no Stable Diffusion, DALL-E, Midjourney etc.)\n- The `meme-maker` skill can create memes\n- I can read/display images\n\nSo the user is right - I don't have image generation capabilities set up yet. Let me be honest about this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"对，目前还没有配置图片生成功能。来看看我现在有什么：\n\n### 现有的图片处理能力\n\n| 能力 | 状态 |\n|------|:----:|\n| **看图/读图** | ✅ 能（用 `read` 读图片内容）|\n| **做梗图** | ⚠️ 有 meme-maker 技能，可以做表情包 |\n| **AI 生成图片** | ❌ 没配置（没有 DALL·E / Stable Diffusion 等）|\n| **图片编辑** | ❌ 没注册功能 |\n\n### 如果你想加一个\"图片生成\"功能\n\n按照 Trinity 的注册流程，可以这样：\n\n1. **你说：** `/注册-图片生成 用 AI 画图`\n2. **Spirit 查** 有没有相似功能\n3. **Spirit 创建** `imagegen_function.md`，定义触发词和调用方式\n4. **你确认** 后生效\n\n不过前提是得先有一个**图片生成的 API 服务**（比如通义万相、Stable Diffusion、DALL·E 等），然后把 API Key 配进来。你有想用的图片生成服务吗？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6249,"output":446,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":196,"totalTokens":52263,"cost":{"input":0.0008748600000000001,"output":0.00012488,"cacheRead":0.001275904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0022756440000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779951940729,"responseId":"4d2edfa5-b1a9-4706-9ee8-5d3f96faa64a"}}
