{"type":"message","id":"91be9c61","parentId":"a335a9e9","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:08:45.609Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to register a new function called \"相册笔记\" (Album Notes). Let me follow the Trinity registration process as defined in AGENTS.md and Trinity.md.\n\nStep 1: Check if similar function exists - I need to spawn Spirit to check bot_function_explain.md\nStep 2: If no similar function, Spirit creates a draft\n\nBut wait - sessions_spawn with agentId spirit was not allowed before. However, I just added `allowAgents: [\"*\"]` to the subagents config. Let me test if I can spawn with agentId now.\n\nActually wait, looking at the sessions_spawn tool description more carefully:\n\n```\nsessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\", task: \"...\")\n```\n\nBut in my previous test, I used `agentId: \"father\"` and it worked. Let me try with \"spirit\" directly.\n\nActually, looking at the sessions_spawn tool parameters:\n- `agentId`: Spawn under another configured agent id when allowed by `subagents.allowAgents`.\n\nSince I set `allowAgents: [\"*\"]`, I should now be able to spawn with agentId \"spirit\". Let me try this.\n\nActually, let me re-read my AGENTS.md carefully for the registration flow:\n\n### 3.1 注册新功能流程\n\n```\n触发: 用户说 \"/注册-xxx 解释内容\" 或明确表达注册意图\n\nStep 1: 检查是否已有相似功能\n  → spawn Spirit，传入用户输入\n     sessions_spawn(agentId: \"spirit\", task: \"用户要注册新功能【xxx】, 描述: ...。请查 bot_function_explain.md 有无相似功能。\")\n  → Spirit 查 bot_function_explain.md\n  → 如有相似功能 → 返回给用户：\"已存在相似功能【xxx】，是否继续注册？\"\n  → 如无 → 继续\n\nStep 2: Spirit 创建 draft\n  → Spirit 创建 xxx_function.md（6段格式）\n  → Spirit 在 bot_function_explain.md 加条目（标记 ⏳）\n  → 返回 draft 内容给我\n\nStep 3: 展示给用户确认\n  → 展示 xxx_function.md 关键内容（触发指令 + 功能说明 + 记录格式）\n  → 询问：\"确认注册【xxx】功能吗？回复'确认'或提出修改意见\"\n\nStep 4: 用户反馈\n  ├─ \"确认\" → 执行三步：\n  ...\n```\n\nSo Step 1: I need to spawn Spirit to check bot_function_explain.md for similar functions.\n\nBut actually, Spirit's files are in `~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/`. I can read `bot_function_explain.md` directly to check for similar functions. Let me do that first.\n\nActually, looking at the AGENTS.md carefully, it says:\n- Step 1: spawn Spirit (not read myself)\n- Step 2: Spirit creates draft\n\nBut for Step 1, I could also just read the file myself since it's simpler. However, the AGENTS.md says to spawn Spirit for this. Let me follow the AGENTS.md.\n\nActually let me think about this differently. I have `allowAgents: [\"*\"]` now. The sessions_spawn tool says `agentId` parameter spawns under another configured agent id. Let me try spawning with agentId \"spirit\".\n\nBut also - looking at my SOUL.md:\n\"❌ 不替 Spirit 编写或修改 `bot_function_explain.md` 和 `xxx_function.md`\"\n\"❌ 不替 Son 执行文件读写操作\"\n\nSo I should let Spirit do its job. Let me spawn Spirit now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！走注册流程，先查查有没有相似功能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Fyj5dNThczeUhImCUSqt7668","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","task":"用户要注册新功能【相册笔记】。\n描述：用户会给图片（在上下文里），也许会附带一些注释。需要存储这张照片，并且按照注释解析图片，一起保存在一个库里。\n\n请做以下两件事：\n\n【Step 1】查 bot_function_explain.md，看看有没有相似功能（比如漂流瓶、备忘录等是否和这个功能类似）。如有相似功能，返回确认信息给我；如无，继续 Step 2。\n\n【Step 2】如无相似功能，请创建相册笔记的功能定义草稿：\n- 在 bot_function_explain.md 底部添加条目（标记 ⏳ 待确认）\n- 创建 album_function.md（按六段格式：功能描述/工作文件夹/触发指令/执行接口/记录格式/返回格式）\n\n创建完后，将 album_function.md 的关键内容（触发指令 + 功能说明 + 记录格式）返回给我。","mode":"run"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"task\": \"用户要注册新功能【相册笔记】。\\n描述：用户会给图片（在上下文里），也许会附带一些注释。需要存储这张照片，并且按照注释解析图片，一起保存在一个库里。\\n\\n请做以下两件事：\\n\\n【Step 1】查 bot_function_explain.md，看看有没有相似功能（比如漂流瓶、备忘录等是否和这个功能类似）。如有相似功能，返回确认信息给我；如无，继续 Step 2。\\n\\n【Step 2】如无相似功能，请创建相册笔记的功能定义草稿：\\n- 在 bot_function_explain.md 底部添加条目（标记 ⏳ 待确认）\\n- 创建 album_function.md（按六段格式：功能描述/工作文件夹/触发指令/执行接口/记录格式/返回格式）\\n\\n创建完后，将 album_function.md 的关键内容（触发指令 + 功能说明 + 记录格式）返回给我。\", \"mode\": \"run\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4