{"type":"message","id":"4005e51e","parentId":"93f3cb01-92a7-43a1-a8c3-a778c8152503","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:12:05.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit has completed its work successfully! Let me summarize what happened:\n\n1. **相似功能检查**: No duplicate/similar functions found ✅\n2. **album_function.md**: Created with full 6-segment format ✅\n3. **bot_function_explain.md**: Entry added with ⏳ pending confirmation ✅\n\nNow according to the registration flow in AGENTS.md, Step 3 is:\n\"展示给用户确认 → 展示 xxx_function.md 关键内容（触发指令 + 功能说明 + 记录格式）→ 询问：'确认注册【相册笔记】功能吗？回复'确认'或提出修改意见'\"\n\nLet me present the draft to the user for confirmation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**Spirit 已完成草稿！** 相似检查无冲突 ✅\n\n以下是 **相册笔记** 的功能草案，请您过目：\n\n---\n\n## 📖 相册笔记 — 功能草案\n\n### 触发指令\n\n| 指令 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `/存照片 [注释文字]` | 存一张照片（需先发图），附带注释和 `#标签` |\n| `/看相册 [标签名]` | 浏览相册，可按标签筛选 |\n| `/搜照片 <关键词>` | 按注释文字搜索 |\n| `/删照片 <ID>` | 删除指定照片 |\n\n### 工作流程示例\n\n```\n你发一张日落照片 + 回复「/存照片 今天拍的夕阳 #夕阳 #摄影」\n\n→ Son 存图到 album/images/\n→ 建 JSON 记录，解析标签\n→ 返回：📸 已存 1 张照片！\n           ID: ALB-20260528-0001\n           注释: \"今天拍的夕阳\"\n           标签: #夕阳 #摄影\n```\n\n### 记录格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"ALB-20260528-0001\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-28T15:10:00+08:00\",\n  \"image\": { \"filename\": \"ALB-20260528-0001.jpg\", ... },\n  \"annotation\": \"今天拍的夕阳，特别美 #夕阳 #摄影\",\n  \"tags\": [\"夕阳\", \"摄影\"]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n**确认注册【相册笔记】功能吗？** 回复 `确认` 或提出修改意见～😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7670,"output":493,"cacheRead":50688,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":143,"totalTokens":58851,"cost":{"input":0.0010738,"output":0.00013804,"cacheRead":0.001419264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002631104}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779952316855,"responseId":"968aec48-319a-4dfe-94ef-56704982e896"}}
