{"type":"message","id":"d14285e8","parentId":"38015bdf","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:12:42.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed the registration of \"相册笔记\" (Album Notes). According to AGENTS.md 3.1 Registration Flow, Step 4:\n\n```\n├─ \"确认\" → 执行三步：\n│\n│  第一步：确认 Spirit 标记\n│    sessions_spawn(\n│      agentId: \"spirit\",\n│      task: \"用户已确认注册【xxx】功能，请将 bot_function_explain.md 中 ⏳ 改为 ✅。确认后回复 done。\"\n│    )\n│\n│  第二步：更新 trigger_prompt.md（我自己写）\n│    → read ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\n│    → 在表格末尾追加新行：\n│       | /xxx /xxx2 | xxx功能 | → Spirit → Son |\n│    → write 回原文件\n│\n│  第三步：通知 Son 创建目录\n│    sessions_spawn(\n│      agentId: \"son\",\n│      task: \"用户已注册【xxx】功能。请在 ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/ 下创建 xxx/ 目录。执行: mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/xxx\"\n│    )\n│\n│  最后回复用户：\n│    \"【xxx】已注册 ✅ 试试 /xxx 吧\"\n```\n\nLet me do all three steps. Step 1: Tell Spirit to update status. Step 2: Update trigger_prompt.md. Step 3: Tell Son to create directory.\n\nLet me start by reading the trigger_prompt.md to see what's there, and simultaneously tell Spirit to update.\n\nLooking at the trigger_prompt.md, I need to determine the trigger words. Based on the album_function.md Spirit created, the triggers are:\n- `/存照片`\n- `/看相册`\n- `/搜照片`\n- `/删照片`\n\nLet me first read the current trigger_prompt.md and simultaneously spawn Spirit to do step 1.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好！开始执行三步确认流程——"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_urLasn6db41HKxoayNUh6691","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"spirit","task":"用户已确认注册【相册笔记】功能。请将 bot_function_explain.md 中对应的 ⏳ 改为 ✅。确认后回复 done。","mode":"run"},"partialArgs":"{\"agentId\": \"spirit\", \"task\": \"用户已确认注册【相册笔记】功能。请将 bot_function_explain.md 中对应的 ⏳ 改为 ✅。确认后回复 done。\", \"mode\": \"run\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_oDVYeNFMuXox6CBynY1Y1132","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_pro