{"type":"message","id":"d24c294f","parentId":"9d98e09a","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:13:47.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit returned the full menu with all 4 registered functions, including the new \"相册笔记\" which is now marked as ✅. Let me forward this to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"📋 **已注册功能一览**（共 4 项）\n\n---\n\n**1️⃣ 漂流瓶 🍶**\n触发：`/扔瓶子` `/捞瓶子` `/看瓶子` `/回复瓶子`\n匿名扔消息到公共瓶海，随机捞取他人的瓶子并回复。\n\n**2️⃣ 备忘录 📒**\n触发：`/记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录`\n个人备忘录，记录、修改、切换状态、删除待办事项。\n\n**3️⃣ 早朝官 🏛️**\n触发：`/早朝` `/设早朝 HH:MM` `/关早朝`\n每天早上自动推送备忘录待办、漂流瓶摘要、童话故事、饮食建议等。\n\n**4️⃣ 相册笔记 📸** 🆕\n触发：`/存照片` `/看相册` `/搜照片` `/删照片`\n接收图片并附注注释文字，解析注释后存入个人相册库，支持搜索和标签浏览。\n\n---\n\n想试试哪个？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4111,"output":258,"cacheRead":55936,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":36,"totalTokens":60305,"cost":{"input":0.00057554,"output":0.00007224,"cacheRead":0.001566208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002213988}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779952424327,"responseId":"65aebc6e-0a16-4e16-9b0b-b11db5e8b7de"}}
