{"type":"message","id":"96d35867","parentId":"719cd89c","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:18:15.521Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"目前环境里没有通义千问的 API Key。请问你的通义千问 API Key 是放在哪里的？我可以几种方式配置：\n\n**方式 A：直接写到 openclaw.json 的 Son 配置里**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"son\",\n  \"workspace\": \"...\",\n  \"subagents\": { \"allowAgents\": [] },\n  \"model\": { \"primary\": \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max\" },\n  \"auth\": { \"profiles\": { ... } }\n}\n```\n\n**方式 B：写成环境变量**\n```bash\nexport DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=***\n```\n然后在 openclaw.json 里 `${DASHSCOPE_API_KEY}` 引用\n\n你有 API Key 在手边吗？给我，我来配～ 或者你说一个你偏好放哪里，我来操作。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":27,"output":182,"cacheRead":57216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57425,"cost":{"input":0.0000037800000000000002,"output":0.00005096000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001602048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001656788}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779952691983,"responseId":"b72edee6-0188-4676-bbb2-8c1f6699b8da"}}
