{"type":"message","id":"ed6a1ed3","parentId":"a08b70cd","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:33:10.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，我认了——我这个模型不能看图，但图片本身存在服务器上没问题。先给你看 `/看相册` 的列表吧：\n\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0001.jpg\nMEDIA:/root/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ALB-20260528-0002.jpg\n\n📖 **相册（共 2 张）**\n\n---\n\n**1️⃣ 南坪快速通道起火 5 27**\n`ALB-20260528-0001` | 📅 2026-05-28 15:15\n📎 无标签\n\n**2️⃣ 开发Openclaw三位一体机器人**\n`ALB-20260528-0002` | 📅 2026-05-28 15:26\n📎 #机器人 #开发\n\n---\n\n上面两张就是照片，能看到缩略图了吗？😄\n\n（后续我会把存储路径统一放到 `workspace-son/album/` 下，再确认一下 `MEDIA` 指令能不能从 Spirit 目录取到图）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":87,"output":246,"cacheRead":81536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81869,"cost":{"input":0.00001218,"output":0.00006888,"cacheRead":0.002283008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002364068}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779953587134,"responseId":"c063be97-099c-483b-886c-e7cf39a3219f"}}
