{"type":"message","id":"f1e4f682","parentId":"14273833","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:34:49.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在在看相册接口里加上 `/看照片` 的执行逻辑："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_LgaUiMpcWpJjtfadIH5I3761","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":30,"offset":44,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album_function.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"limit\": 30, \"offset\": 44, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album_function.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":155,"output":101,"cacheRead":82688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82944,"cost":{"input":0.000021700000000000002,"output":0.00002828,"cacheRead":0.002315264,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002365244}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779953687485,"responseId":"cfe6e284-fd18-4950-9a37-c12f3ae5d8a7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0a4efc8","parentId":"f1e4f682","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:34:49.823Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_LgaUiMpcWpJjtfadIH5I3761","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 4.2 看相册 (list)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 读取 `album/data/` 目录下所有 JSON 文件\n2. 如果指定了标签名参数，筛选包含该标签的记录\n3. 按时间倒序排列（最新的在前）\n4. 返回列表给 Father（每张照片显示 ID、注释摘要、标签、时间）\n5. 限制一次最多返回 20 条\n\n### 4.3 搜照片 (search)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 读取 `album/data/` 目录下所有 JSON 文件\n2. 筛选 `annotation` 字段中包含关键词的记录（不区分大小写）\n3. 按时间倒序排列\n4. 返回匹配结果给 Father（显示 ID、注释摘要、标签、时间、匹配的部分）\n5. 限制一次最多返回 20 条\n\n### 4.4 删照片 (delete)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\"未找到该照片记录\"\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名\n4. 删除 `album/images/{文件名}` 和 `album/data/{ID}.json`\n5. 返回删除成功\n\n## 5. 记录格式规范\n\n### 文件命名\nJSON 记录：`ALB-YYYYMMDD-NNNN.json`\n图片文件：`ALB-YYYYMMDD-NNNN.{ext}`（ext 保持原扩展名，如 jpg/png/gif/webp）\n\n\n[99 more lines in file. Use offset=74 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779953689822}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ff27919","parentId":"b0a4efc8","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:34:53.899Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_imId9Wd6zq70liLDSpxN5189","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album_function.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 4.4 删照片 (delete)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\"未找到该照片记录\"\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名\n4. 删除 `album/images/{文件名}` 和 `album/data/{ID}.json`\n5. 返回删除成功","newText":"### 4.4 看照片 (view)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\"未找到该照片\"\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名和记录信息\n4. 返回结果时在文本前加上 `MEDIA:album/images/{文件名}` 指令，Father 收到后单独发送图片到聊天中\n5. 同时返回该照片的记录信息（注释、标签、时间）\n\n### 4.5 删照片 (delete)\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\"未找到该照片记录\"\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名\n4. 删除 `album/images/{文件名}` 和 `album/data/{ID}.json`\n5. 返回删除成功"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album_function.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"### 4.4 删照片 (delete)\\nSon 执行步骤:\\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\\\"未找到该照片记录\\\"\\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名\\n4. 删除 `album/images/{文件名}` 和 `album/data/{ID}.json`\\n5. 返回删除成功\",\"newText\":\"### 4.4 看照片 (view)\\nSon 执行步骤:\\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\\\"未找到该照片\\\"\\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名和记录信息\\n4. 返回结果时在文本前加上 `MEDIA:album/images/{文件名}` 指令，Father 收到后单独发送图片到聊天中\\n5. 同时返回该照片的记录信息（注释、标签、时间）\\n\\n### 4.5 删照片 (delete)\\nSon 执行步骤:\\n1. 检查 `album/data/{ID}.json` 是否存在\\n2. 如不存在，返回错误\\\"未找到该照片记录\\\"\\n3. 如存在，读取图片文件名\\n4. 删除 `album/images/{文件名}` 和 `album/data/{ID}.json`\\n5. 返回删除成功\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":363,"output":372,"cacheRead":82944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83679,"cost":{"input":0.000050820000000000005,"output":0.00010416,"cacheRead":0.002322432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002477412}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779953689841,"responseId":"cef0a393-7b3b-4539-95ea-b6a333cd5354"}}
