{"type":"message","id":"17a59ac3","parentId":"37d07503","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:36:22.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"图片能读但是发不出来。两个问题需要修复：\n\n**问题 1：MEDIA 指令的路径不对**\nFather 的 `MEDIA:` 指令需要**绝对路径**或可从 Father 访问到的路径，而图片在 Spirit 的目录里。\n\n**问题 2：图片存错地方了**\n按照 album_function.md 设计，图片应该存在 Son 的 `album/images/` 下，但实际存在 Spirit 的目录了。\n\n我先修一下，把图移到 Son 目录，再统一配置路径："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KXChxf0MaQWlOIN3KuiM6935","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 1. 创建 Son 的 album 目录\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data\n\n# 2. 把现有照片和记录从 Spirit 移到 Son\ncp -r ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/* ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/\ncp -r ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/* ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data/\n\n# 3. 检查\necho \"=== Son album目录 ===\"\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data/\n\necho \"=== Spirit album目录 ===\"\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ 2>/dev/null\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"# 1. 创建 Son 的 album 目录\\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images\\nmkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data\\n\\n# 2. 把现有照片和记录从 Spirit 移到 Son\\ncp -r ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/* ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/\\ncp -r ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/* ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data/\\n\\n# 3. 检查\\necho \\\"=== Son album目录 ===\\\"\\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/images/\\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/album/data/\\n\\necho \\\"=== Spirit album目录 ===\\\"\\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/images/ 2>/dev/null\\nls -la ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/album/data/ 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":110,"output":382,"cacheRead":86400,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86892,"cost":{"input":0.0000154,"outp