{"type":"message","id":"7e26d5b8","parentId":"b9859638","timestamp":"2026-05-28T07:46:35.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📖 **相册（共 3 张）**\n\n**1️⃣** 按照图片写一首短诗\n`ALB-20260528-0003` | 🏷️ #星海 | 📅 2026-05-28 15:43\n\n**2️⃣** 开发Openclaw三位一体机器人\n`ALB-20260528-0002` | 🏷️ #机器人 #开发 | 📅 2026-05-28 15:26\n\n**3️⃣** 南坪快速通道起火 5 27\n`ALB-20260528-0001` | 🏷️ 无标签 | 📅 2026-05-28 15:15\n\n---\n\n📌 查看图片：`/看照片 序号`（如 `/看照片 1` 看最新那张）\n🔍 搜索：`/搜照片 <关键词>`\n🏷️ 标签浏览：`/看相册 #星海`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2115,"output":212,"cacheRead":89728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92055,"cost":{"input":0.00029610000000000004,"output":0.00005936,"cacheRead":0.002512384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002867844}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779954392156,"responseId":"aa764810-1e2a-4a7a-9c6b-d08fea4f6593"}}
