{"type":"message","id":"76f0e351","parentId":"9d97424e","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:06:57.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了！**多个 QQ Bot 账号**（每个有自己的 AppID）。\n\n那推荐**方案 2：每个 Bot 一套 Trinity**。架构大概长这样：\n\n```\n               ┌─ Bot A（你的主号）\n               │   appId: 1904085484\n               │   └─ Father_A → Spirit_A → Son_A\n               │       (workspace-father-a)\nQQ 用户 ← 多Bot ── Bot B（给别人用）\n               │   appId: xxxxxx\n               │   └─ Father_B → Spirit_B → Son_B\n               │       (workspace-father-b)\n               │\n               └─ Bot C（测试号）\n                   appId: xxxxxx\n                   └─ Father_C → Spirit_C → Son_C\n                       (workspace-father-c)\n```\n\n### 配置变动\n\n每个 Bot 配自己的 `channels.qqbot` 条目：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"qqbot\": {\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"bot_a\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904085484\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        },\n        \"bot_b\": {\n          \"appId\": \"xxxxx\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    { \"agentId\": \"father_a\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot_a\" } },\n    { \"agentId\": \"father_b\", \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot_b\" } }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n每个 Father 有独立的：\n- `User.md`（用户画像）\n- `workspace-son/`（相册、漂流瓶等数据完全隔离）\n\n---\n\n你是打算先搞个测试号试试，还是已经有另一个 Bot 账号的 AppID 在手上了？要开搞的话我可以帮你搭起来~ 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1693,"output":416,"cacheRead":90880,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92989,"cost":{"input":0.00023702,"output":0.00011648000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00254464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00289814}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779955611188,"responseId":"f51a76e3-6e91-4b83-8e88-cd7c2bcd048b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"393f7232","parentId":"76f0e351","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:08:26.281Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"不要这样，共用一个father，一套流程，但有些功能要做公私之分，比如备忘录是各用户私有 漂流瓶就是共有池了","timestamp":1779955704003}}
{"type":"message","id":"810760e2","parentId":"393f7232","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:08:33.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了！**一个 Father，一套 Trinity 流程**，功能按 **公有 vs 私有** 划分：\n\n```\n                ┌─ Bot A ──┐\nQQ 用户 ──多个Bot ── Bot B ───┼─→ Father（统一入口）\n                └─ Bot C ──┘\n                              │\n                      ┌───────┴───────┐\n                      │   判断功能     │\n                      └───────┬───────┘\n                              │\n         ┌────────────────────┼────────────────────┐\n         ↓ 私有               ↓ 公有               ↓ 私有\n      备忘录                漂流瓶              相册笔记\n      (按 sender_id 分)    (共用一个池)        (按 sender_id 分)\n```\n\n### 当前注册的功能归类\n\n| 功能 | 类型 | 数据隔离方式 |\n|------|:----:|------------|\n| **备忘录** | 🔒 私有 | 每条记录标 sender_id，各用户只看自己的 |\n| **相册笔记** | 🔒 私有 | 同上，各人存各人的照片 |\n| **漂流瓶** | 🌐 公有 | 所有人共享一个瓶海 |\n| **早朝官** | 🔒 私有 | 各人收各人的推送 |\n\n现在的核心改动是：**数据记录里加 `sender_id`**。\n\n比如备忘录 JSON 现在是这样：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"MEMO-xxx\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6687D4D2...\",\n  \"content\": \"...\"\n}\n```\n\n漂流瓶就不加 sender_id 的限制，谁都能捞谁的。\n\n那我需要现在就开始改各个 `xxx_function.md` 和 Son 的执行逻辑，把 `sender_id` 字段加上去。要搞吗？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1504,"output":388,"cacheRead":91520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93412,"cost":{"input":0.00021056000000000002,"output":0.00010864,"cacheRead":0.0025625599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028817599999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779955706454,"responseId":"8400eed8-47fc-43f0-b5fe-013f04269352"}}
