8601 | ✅ | 最后更新时间 |\\n| status | string | ✅ | pending 待办 / completed 已完成 / deleted 已删除 |\",\"newText\":\"### JSON 结构\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"id\\\": 1,\\n  \\\"content\\\": \\\"备忘录内容\\\",\\n  \\\"sender_id\\\": \\\"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\\",\\n  \\\"created_at\\\": \\\"2026-05-28T12:00:00+08:00\\\",\\n  \\\"updated_at\\\": \\\"2026-05-28T12:00:00+08:00\\\",\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"pending\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### 字段说明\\n\\n| 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 说明 |\\n|------|------|:--:|------|\\n| id | number | ✅ | 唯一序号（按用户独立，不同用户从1开始） |\\n| content | string | ✅ | 备忘录内容 |\\n| sender_id | string | ✅ | 用户 QQ ID，用于按用户隔离数据 |\\n| created_at | ISO-8601 | ✅ | 创建时间 |\\n| updated_at | ISO-8601 | ✅ | 最后更新时间 |\\n| status | string | ✅ | pending 待办 / completed 已完成 / deleted 已删除 |\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":165,"output":580,"cacheRead":101376,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102121,"cost":{"input":0.000023100000000000002,"output":0.00016240000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002838528,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003024028}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779955771827,"responseId":"75cebabe-aa9b-4c4e-a95e-c584079952c5"}}
