{"type":"message","id":"19221400","parentId":"39decafa","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:10:35.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"全部完成 ✅\n\n### 🔄 改了什么？\n\n| 功能 | 类型 | 改动 |\n|:----:|:----:|------|\n| 🍶 **漂流瓶** | 🌐 **公有** | JSON 记录加 `sender_id` 用于溯源，但**所有人共享瓶海** |\n| 📒 **备忘录** | 🔒 **私有** | 所有操作按 sender_id 过滤，各人只看/改/删自己的条目 |\n| 📸 **相册笔记** | 🔒 **私有** | 所有操作按 sender_id 过滤，各人存各人的照片 |\n| 🏛️ **早朝官** | 🔒 **私有** | config 按 sender_id 分文件，读备忘录时过滤当前用户 |\n| 👨‍👧 **Father** | — | spawn Spirit 时必须传 `sender_id` |\n\n### 现有数据已打上你的 sender_id ✅\n\n以后多 Bot 进来，各自用各自的 QQ ID，**私有数据不串、公有池共享**，完美符合你的设计~ 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":195,"output":225,"cacheRead":108672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109092,"cost":{"input":0.000027300000000000003,"output":0.000063,"cacheRead":0.003042816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003133116}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779955831492,"responseId":"b69053d2-1af1-41c1-b536-41d5cc26e858"}}
