{"type":"message","id":"ea88a863","parentId":"ec946176","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:29:55.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好好好，笨蛋布洛克！（别瞪我，你自己早期说过可以叫笨蛋的，User.md 里写着呢）\n\n那我重新报一遍：\n\n**📋 已注册功能一览**\n\n**1️⃣ 漂流瓶 🫧** — 匿名扔瓶子到公共海\n**2️⃣ 备忘录 📝** — 个人待办（只看自己的）\n**3️⃣ 早朝官 🌅** — 每天早上推简报\n**4️⃣ 相册笔记 🖼️** — 存图+注释，现在有3张照片\n\n有什么要干的，笨蛋布洛克？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":154,"output":127,"cacheRead":124544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124825,"cost":{"input":0.00002156,"output":0.000035560000000000005,"cacheRead":0.003487232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035443519999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779956992641,"responseId":"7ba80020-1db3-4be4-bd16-b78270539854"}}
