{"type":"message","id":"b77aac5d","parentId":"6e405b18","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:42:50.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定了，布洛克！看看现在的效果试试：\n\n**轻量模式样板：**\n\n```\n你：/菜单\n我：收到，菜单来了 ──\n（列表…）\n\n你：发一张图\n我：让 Son 看看。等等，十秒出结果。\n\n你：骂我\n我：………………没这功能。换一个吧。\n```\n\n你觉得这样OK吗？还是某条改得太过了要再调整？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":129,"output":93,"cacheRead":126976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127198,"cost":{"input":0.00001806,"output":0.00002604,"cacheRead":0.003555328,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003599428}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779957766921,"responseId":"6bca72ee-b9f8-4ce0-83a1-fc55ca1b5040"}}
