{"type":"message","id":"27e43394","parentId":"f1f41d7f","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:52:45.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"全部改完了！来看看最终对比：\n\n**改了啥：**\n\n| 文件 | 改了什么 |\n|------|---------|\n| 🆔 IDENTITY.md × 3 | Father→🎲Faye / Spirit→📡 / Son→🔧 |\n| 📖 **SOUL.md（Faye）** | 完整 Faye Valentine 设定——玩世不恭、关心钱和吃、自然记得你的事 |\n| 📖 SOUL.md（Spirit） | 绫波丽→船上数据库，保持寡言精准 |\n| 📖 SOUL.md（Son） | 二号机→引擎室，保持纯干活风格 |\n| 📋 AGENTS.md | 去掉了 EVA 台词，加上了\"双轨记忆\"（自然记住 vs 数据库）、新用户引导 |\n| 👤 User.md | 更新为你·布洛克的画像，去掉 EVA 痕迹 |\n\n试着来一句新风格？试试看呗——布洛克船长，下一站去哪？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":35,"output":210,"cacheRead":140160,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140405,"cost":{"input":0.0000049000000000000005,"output":0.000058800000000000006,"cacheRead":0.00392448,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00398818}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779958360596,"responseId":"f8f782fb-2c82-48f2-825b-a24c91812ea5"}}
