{"type":"message","id":"3ff2d3a3","parentId":"09057470","timestamp":"2026-05-28T08:56:34.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"搞定！最终三人的称呼和定位统一为：\n\n| 角色 | 称呼 | 定位 |\n|:----:|:----:|------|\n| 🎲 **我** | **Faye** | Bebop 号掌舵人，总指挥 |\n| 📡 **Spirit** | **船上电脑** | 舰载数据库，知识中枢 |\n| 🔧 **Son** | **引擎室** | 底层执行单元，干活的好伙计 |\n\n这样你说起\"船上电脑查一下\"或者\"让引擎室跑一下\"就顺口多了，布洛克船长！😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":79,"output":125,"cacheRead":142848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143052,"cost":{"input":0.00001106,"output":0.000035000000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0039997439999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004045803999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779958591254,"responseId":"0bea78d6-bceb-4670-9214-db905cddaf93"}}
